<p begin="24690000t" end="39590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40700000t" end="73690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74740000t" end="142430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260590000t" end="303930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304970000t" end="373350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415410000t" end="496760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="517180000t" end="531510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532530000t" end="565860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566890000t" end="618880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619950000t" end="668980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670000000t" end="730980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="801130000t" end="831050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第6話 破綻&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="944610000t" end="953250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;我是L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="958950000t" end="973280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;這個男的就是…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="981310000t" end="998260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;總覺得跟想像差太多了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1039030000t" end="1057000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;我是警察廳的夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1064730000t" end="1084980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;我是松田&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我是相澤&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1086080000t" end="1104390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;我是模木&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我是宇生田&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1121780000t" end="1138050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;抱歉我們來晚了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1139130000t" end="1155400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;我們五位是目前…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1178510000t" end="1189770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;你在比劃些什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1206870000t" end="1248850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;我若是KIRA的話,你就死定囉&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;夜神總一郎先生&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1265260000t" end="1297910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;KIRA殺人的必要條件&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是長相和姓名&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1298960000t" end="1329560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;這一點你們應該都知道了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1330660000t" end="1357620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;所以請別隨便說出自己的姓名&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1358690000t" end="1377690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;要好好珍惜生命啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1401730000t" end="1417310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;我知道長相是必要條件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1418410000t" end="1449350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;但是,有說過姓名也需要嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1455780000t" end="1499470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;那些曾被報導過,但姓名不詳&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1500490000t" end="1541790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;或者搞錯姓名的重刑犯&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;全部都免於一死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1542870000t" end="1563460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;這些事在搜查總部就說過了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1570230000t" end="1595140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;別光站著說話,都請過來吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1604260000t" end="1613930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;是…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1614940000t" end="1649860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;請將手機或手提電腦&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;及其他通訊器材關機後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1650980000t" end="1668610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;放到那邊的桌子上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1683680000t" end="1715650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;L,你是懷疑我們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;會將手機設定為通話狀態&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1716710000t" end="1729680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;然後把談話內容洩漏給外界嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1730720000t" end="1749030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;好了,就按照他說的去做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1759420000t" end="1783760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;雖然他一開始就十分小心謹慎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1784780000t" end="1811740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;但我們到底&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有沒有得到他的信任啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1812810000t" end="1869810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;不,我只是不能容忍自己說話時&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被手機聲打斷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1878200000t" end="1894470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;事先聲明一下&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1895560000t" end="1921840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;我在這個總部所說過的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1922920000t" end="1958870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;都不可以作筆記或什麼的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而是要記在腦海裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1971970000t" end="1995290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;請吧,大家隨便坐&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2232230000t" end="2242120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;那個,L…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2243240000t" end="2267920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;從現在開始請不要叫我L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2268930000t" end="2299190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;叫我龍崎,以防萬一&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2308970000t" end="2325240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;那麼龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2326320000t" end="2351000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;既然已經知道長相和名字&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是必要條件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2352010000t" end="2370660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;那麼如果限制罪犯的報導&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2371700000t" end="2395700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;不就能減少犧牲者了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2396720000t" end="2426070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;如果那樣做&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被殺害的就會是一般人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2427090000t" end="2449390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;一般人?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;為什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2472800000t" end="2496120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;因為KIRA是個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;幼稚又爭強好勝的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2497160000t" end="2528440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;幼稚…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;爭強好勝…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2529520000t" end="2566490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;是的,我也是個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;幼稚而又爭強好勝的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2567560000t" end="2579840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;所以我能瞭解他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2592250000t" end="2634910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;龍崎,能不能說得白話一點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2647310000t" end="2683940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;我在電視上向KIRA宣戰時&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2695020000t" end="2730630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;之前一直被認為&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只會殺罪犯的KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2731720000t" end="2761070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;竟毫不猶豫的殺了我的替身&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2771430000t" end="2808060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;然後我說他就潛藏在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;日本的關東地區&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2809130000t" end="2828470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;他就像在對我說:「那又如何?」似的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2829490000t" end="2861800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;開始以全國的罪犯為中心&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;展開了殺戮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2896220000t" end="2944910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;他完全不畏懼我的挑釁&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;反而很強硬的反過來挑釁我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2945940000t" end="2964250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;對有如此舉動的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2965290000t" end="2988270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;用限制報導來隱藏罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2989310000t" end="3007280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;你認為他會作何反應&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3008330000t" end="3018000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;那個…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3027350000t" end="3057950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;如果不交出罪人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那就殺掉罪輕的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3059050000t" end="3081000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;甚或是殺死無罪之人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3082070000t" end="3106980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;全世界的人都是人質&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3116440000t" end="3136350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;錯不在我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3137460000t" end="3176480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;違逆我,藏匿罪人的你們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;才是罪惡的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3203860000t" end="3227180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;這就是KIRA的思維&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3228220000t" end="3262230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;既然如此&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;倒不如考慮利用一下媒體&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3263260000t" end="3272580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;比如說呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3279940000t" end="3296890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;這樣如何呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3304960000t" end="3332940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;因為殺了FBI探員而惹惱美國&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3333990000t" end="3354920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;KIRA引起全世界的憤怒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3356010000t" end="3395600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;各先進國家要派遣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;1500名探員進駐日本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3403060000t" end="3442990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;不僅是之前的FBI探員&#x202c;</p>
